maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
1-0-8-8, Wild: 8
(one, zero, eight, eight; Wild: eight)
